metadata.name: Down the Rabbit Hole
metadata.description:
Th world I had scrutinised for so long was all around me,as if I had leaned forward and plunged into something unique, adventurous..I have no idea how deep this ride be..But am sure to unravel this mystery and fix the forgotten details.. 

Down the Rabbit Hole is my genesis on AI exploration, trying to find new realm in art world, and journey has started and am a curious little Alice in a wonderland of Art travelling down that rabbit hole.
Created this illustration using multiple AI generated images and painting in Procreate.
